I say, in the name of Jesus, for their eyes to be enlightened with light.

00:27:21.619 --> 00:27:27.319
I thank You for angelic visitations and manifestations of glory.

00:27:27.320 --> 00:27:33.073
Use the person who's just in the marketplace, working on their jobs.

00:27:33.074 --> 00:27:40.193
Father, when they lay hands on the sick, just like You said in Your Word, they would recover.

00:27:40.194 --> 00:27:47.243
I thank You, Father, for this last call, for this last outpouring.

00:27:47.244 --> 00:27:51.562
We call forth Elon Musk today. We say: will you pray for him for 20 days?

00:27:51.563 --> 00:27:57.600
That Elon Musk would be radically born again, filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:27:57.601 --> 00:28:09.861
