I thank You, Father, that Donald Trump has a fire in him. God, I pray for gasoline on that supernatural fire in Jesus'name. Stir and stir, Holy Spirit!

00:28:36.061 --> 00:28:47.735
Stir in that family with great divine protection according to Psalm 91, that a thousand shall fall at their side and ten thousand at their right hand, but nothing shall come nigh them.

