No plots or plans of the wicked will be successful. We call forth a divine angelic visitation of protection over every one of the family members, over the Vice President, and over the President.

00:29:11.873 --> 00:29:19.413
And we thank You, Lord, for the ones we have in there now—I thank You, Lord, that they don't do anything else corrupt while they're in there.

