I thank You, Father, that You're coming soon. Jesus is coming.

00:30:22.567 --> 00:30:44.619
We should be busy about doing what the Father's called us to do—occupy until He comes. Being bold and radical about the Father's business.

00:30:44.620 --> 00:30:55.599
Just like Paul Revere in the night, saying, 'The British are coming!'Father, we would stand in the darkness on our horse, saying, 'Jesus is coming!

00:30:55.600 --> 00:31:10.802
Jesus is coming!'Calling forth the men and women and women getting ready for the soon return of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:31:10.803 --> 00:31:27.967
Because there is a great battle ahead to win the lost. When the anointing comes on me, I yell.

00:31:27.968 --> 00:31:43.725
Thank You, Father, for a supernatural move of Your presence around the world one last time.

00:31:43.726 --> 00:31:51.665
Thank You, Lord, for protecting the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade today. Thank You, Lord, that no calamity comes nigh.

00:31:51.666 --> 00:32:04.518
Thank You, Lord, that nothing happens at the Rockin'New Year's Eve, and that tomorrow, whenever people are Black Friday shopping, no weapon formed against the people will prosper.

00:32:04.519 --> 00:32:26.999
I thank You, Lord, that people are protected. Lord, we give You all the glory, honor, and praise for it in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:32:27.000 --> 00:32:41.429
Amen. Well, thank you for coming and praying with me today. I know it's a shorter video, but I wanted to make it where you could go and spend time with your families.

00:32:41.430 --> 00:33:20.355
If you don't live in America and you don't celebrate Thanksgiving, celebrate it where you are. Be thankful today. If you're new here, we pray every day.

00:33:20.356 --> 00:33:35.879
Diana and I are praying together, believing with you for your healings, for anything that you have need of.

00:33:35.880 --> 00:34:11.376
Nothing's too big for God. All things are possible to him who believes.

00:34:11.377 --> 00:34:19.120
Subscribe to our videos if you haven't ever subscribed before.

00:34:19.121 --> 00:34:23.838
We're just people that love Jesus, children of the Most High God.

00:34:23.839 --> 00:35:03.253
We believe in our covenant, that Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever. We stand with you. Prayer changes things.

00:35:03.254 --> 00:35:16.914
Subscribe, click the notification bell, click the like button—do all the things that YouTube asks us to do—and we will see you tomorrow.

00:35:16.915 --> 00:35:23.981
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart; Jesus loves you so much, and we love you.

00:35:23.982 --> 00:35:31.640
God bless you all, and we will see you again tomorrow. Bye-bye.

